entries.arrived_at_delivery: You are at the correct location pilot, the freighter should be there any second.
entries.attack_notify: Tactical Computer: < Incoming fighter vessels. Scans show weapons armed. >
entries.attack_stopped: Tactical Computer: < No more fighter vessels within sensor range. >
entries.autorewardbody: Good job with the delivery to Dantooine. I'll make sure Johnson Smith knows you did well. I've enclosed the delivery fee.
entries.docking_complete_delivery: I got it. I'll radio Kara and let her know the goods have been delivered.
entries.docking_started_delivery: Lets do this quickly, I don't like the look of all those laser burns on your ship.
entries.failed_destroyed: Return to Kara immediately pilot. She can schedule another delivery.
entries.found_loc_d: Deliver the shipment to the freighter at these coordinates.
entries.hello_d: Greetings, I'm ready to transfer your cargo to my ship.
entries.quest_dock2_d: Make sure that you have eliminated nearby threats before starting the docking sequence as both you and the freighter will be very vulnerable during the transfer.
entries.quest_location_d: A freighter will meet with you in the Dantooine System.
entries.quest_rendezvous2_d: You have been provided with these coordinates for the delivery. Try to avoid any bandits or pirates in the area.
entries.split_quest_alert: Your next delivery is in the Tatooine System. We'll send an updated location once you arrive there.
entries.title: Dantooine System: Make Kara's Dantooine delivery.
entries.title_d: Deliver Kara's shipment of goods to a freighter in the Datooine System.
